{"tid":804584,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"劇透 蠟筆小新功夫小子拉麵大亂鬥 隱喻","createTime":"2018-09-03T06:38:25.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-13T13:37:41.000Z","uid":74778,"like":7,"dislike":15,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9ddc1dd46ad1d6ebe5b1f3343acf4245bd6c1a49","tid":804584,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T06:38:25.000Z","msg":"佛教隱喻<br />\n<br />\n1.<br />\n文化流動係由中東及印度傳到中國再傳入日本<br />\n所以中國有當天竺(印度)神咁拜去取西經<br />\n小新就由日本去成都取西經<br />\n<br />\n同西遊記一樣，唐僧 孫悟空 豬八戒 沙僧4人加白馬取西經<br />\n蠟筆小新有，玉蘭 小新 爸爸 媽媽 加小白去成都取西經<br />\n<br />\n柔軟彈彈精靈係參照印度教濕婆神既外貌設計<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/142712_d2df472254e7f9dcfe4c54ac3668b8b3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F142712_d2df472254e7f9dcfe4c54ac3668b8b3.png&h=ae9319b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/03/142714_772f809328019036d10dfce4817cf3de.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F03%2F142714_772f809328019036d10dfce4817cf3de.png&h=3bb7b9ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n2. <br />\n柔軟彈彈，唔係淨係功夫，仲要講求柔軟彈彈既心<br />\n玉蘭因為太執著正義同邪惡，所以走火入魔，最後玉蘭放下執著先大團圓結局。<br />\n<br />\n結論係呢套係一套佛教電影，呼籲人要放下執著，用暴力達到既和平不是和平，而係透過宣揚柔軟彈彈精神(佛法)，令人人都柔軟不競爭，先達到世界和平。<br />\n<br />\n利申，鳩嗡"},{"pid":"5fbc76b16aafd69c486ce5ac97bad86600d7fd42","tid":804584,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T07:41:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbb3852c5727b231ed851fdfe24a96048d6c830e","tid":804584,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:29:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3c111983381fb672d1b24ff4c1f6e1b16e7f0ee","tid":804584,"uid":16635,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T08:45:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"45791ba385e4dde16dc0b4a934610937fc514fd2","tid":804584,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T09:09:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85064071567e1deb84851f0aee8cd420c360c2a0","tid":804584,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-03T10:18:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5f5eef0296bbeca502ac6f9c785c82ef0115bd20","tid":804584,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:28:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1765460313afcc33b43bb609e2032cafc727e2ea","tid":804584,"uid":121580,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T00:33:28.000Z","msg":"和而不同,同而不和<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec2906f7202ce955e71e74a0feed9f70e4ce8a32","tid":804584,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-04T10:46:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"65c9c3f9c82eb602b39025afcdc5c1a43509d272","tid":804584,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T03:14:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c39edc28b0c87cfe64f2106de149f46ac6932ed","tid":804584,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T08:51:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5e828580538522d712eef051290b1dc2dd7cc13","tid":804584,"uid":74778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-12T10:54:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b262e2c05fd1eaef274d6a4164bf2